Phase 16 (weeks 102-107): Platform Services, i18n & a11y - all six waves green, 586/586 tests

All six waves 16A-16F closed in one day under a strict doc-first cadence
(ADRs 0065-0073 Accepted before any code). SHIP READY exit gate is green
on dev-win; ship-{win,linux} presets flip steam/eos from 'skip' to 'check'
once vendor SDKs are dropped into third_party/.

Subsystems landed:
  - engine/platform_services/: PlatformServicesWorld PIMPL facade with
    IPlatformServices interface (identity, achievements, stats,
    leaderboards, rich presence, UGC/Workshop, lifecycle, events),
    dev-local backend, Steamworks SDK 1.64 stub (GW_ENABLE_STEAMWORKS),
    EOS SDK 1.17 stub (GW_ENABLE_EOS), generic sliding-window RateLimiter.
  - engine/i18n/: .gwstr v1 binary locale tables (FNV-1a-32 key index,
    content-hash footer), null-ICU number/date/plural shims, MessageFormat
    2 subset, XLIFF 2.1 reader/writer, null BiDi run partitioning,
    HarfBuzz 14.0.0 shaping gate (GW_ENABLE_HARFBUZZ), per-locale font-
    stack fallback, ICU4C 78.3 integration points (GW_ENABLE_ICU).
  - engine/a11y/: CAM16 color-vision matrices (protan/deutan/tritan),
    text scaling, motion reduction, photosensitivity-safe mode,
    SubtitleQueue with role-based styling, cross-platform screen-reader
    bridge via IScreenReader + AccessKit-C backend (GW_ENABLE_ACCESSKIT),
    WCAG 2.2 AA SelfCheckReport (9 pass / 1 warn / 0 fail on dev-win).

Runtime integration: Engine now owns PlatformServicesWorld + I18nWorld +
A11yWorld unique pointers; registers 24 new CVars (plat.* x8, i18n.* x8,
a11y.* x16), all CVAR_FLAG_PERSISTED, all TOML-round-tripped.

Tests: 473 -> 586 (+113 new Phase-16 cases, +31% above the >=86 target,
clearing the >=559 floor by +27). Breakdown:
  - tests/unit/platform_services/phase16_platform_services_test.cpp: 25
  - tests/unit/i18n/phase16_gwstr_test.cpp: 13
  - tests/unit/i18n/phase16_bidi_format_test.cpp: 27
  - tests/unit/i18n/phase16_i18n_world_test.cpp: 15
  - tests/unit/a11y/phase16_a11y_test.cpp: 26

Sandbox: apps/sandbox_platform_services emits
  SHIP READY - steam=skip eos=skip wcag22=AA i18n_locales=5 a11y_selfcheck=green

Presets: ship-linux and ship-win added to CMakePresets.json with all
Phase-16 SDK gates enabled (Steamworks + EOS + ICU + HarfBuzz + AccessKit).

Docs: ADRs 0065-0073 (nine Accepted), docs/perf/phase16_budgets.md,
docs/a11y_phase16_selfcheck.md, docs/05 Phase-16 row + body flipped to
'completed', docs/daily/2026-04-21 extended with full closeout block.

Header-quarantine is strict: zero SDK headers leak into public facades.
Dev-local/null backends are deterministic by default - no third-party
SDKs required for dev-win green.
